    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: speed.x
      value: 200
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: coyoteTime
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _explanation
      value: 'Platformer controller

        ----------------

        Platformer
        movement; horizontal speed is 200 units per second.

        Horizontal movement
        will be controlled by the [Horizontal] axis.

        Ground check is going
        to use collider GroundCheck, the ground layer mask defines what is considered
        solid ground.

        When there''s no solid ground below character, the
        character will fall with a gravity scale of 5.

        The character''s
        trajectory can be modified mid-air.

        When in the air, the character''s
        collider will be Player(Player (UnityEngine.BoxCollider2D)), and on the ground
        will be Player(Player (UnityEngine.CapsuleCollider2D)).

        The character
        will not jump (it can still fall).

        This controller also controls
        some visuals:

        When the player intent is to go left, the horizontal
        scale of this object will be inverted.

        Some values will be set on
        animator Player:

        Horizontal velocity will be set to parameter VelocityX.

        Absolute
        horizontal velocity will be set to parameter AbsVelocityX.

        Vertical
        velocity will be set to parameter VelocityY.

        Absolute vertical velocity
        will be set to parameter AbsVelocityY.

        Grounded state will be set
        to parameter IsGrounded.

'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: gravityScale
      value: 5
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: maxJumpCount
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
